<beginCreatedObjects>
<beginStartingNarrative>
This game shows how Non-Functional Requirements (NFRs) affect effort estimation using a linear regression model. 

You are given 10 project scenarios, each with different Non-Functional Requirements (NFRs). For each scenario, you select the most appropriate effort estimation range. 

PLAY THE INTERACTIVE GAME: 

Access the game here 
https://chairegestionproduitsprojetslogiciels.github.io/simse-software-estimation-capability/questionnaires/game-3-questionnaire.html 

The questionnaire will guide you through each scenario with: 
- Interactive NFR tables 
- Automatic weight calculation 
- Visual range selection on the regression graph 

Once you've selected your range for each scenario, return to SimSE to submit your answers (1-5). 
<endStartingNarrative>
